         <abstract id="aspace_d71d4ded5474773107b21c3e4d1b9dc8">The collection consists of a manuscript, printed materials, postcards, and photographs relating to the history of Algeria and the current political, economic, and social conditions.</abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_bfe94df2ba284ab97189d03544ba63c3">
            <language>The material is in English and French.</language>
         </langmaterial>
    
