         <p>The material in the original accession is arranged chronologically, with photographs last. The arrangement of later accessions may vary.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_523fe38ebbaad901a97bd61fb7671cbe">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of a manuscript, printed materials, postcards, and photographs relating to the history of Algeria and the current political, economic, and social conditions.</p>  
